  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The number of breast cancer survivors is growing. Women with a personal history of breast
      cancer worry about their risk of getting cancer again. The current study will develop
      counseling about breast cancer recurrence risk and will also get an estimate of the
      preliminary impact of this counseling. The goal is to enable women to make better decisions
      about their treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
