    <measure>Comparative Perceived Risk of Breast Cancer</measure>
    <time_frame>6 months</time_frame>
    <description>Comparative perceived risk will be assessed with a comparative risk item (i.e., compared those of the same gender and race; Lipkus, CEBP 2000).</description>
